{
  "texts": [
    "Inspired by this idea, Jiang et al. (2023c) propose two methods for determining the timing of retrieval.",
    "The first method involves interrupting the generation of the LM when it encounters a place where a retrieval needs to be performed and then performing the retrieval operation.",
    "The second method involves generating a temporary sentence in its entirety.",
    "If there is a low confidence marker in the sentence, the marker is masked and the rest of the sentence is used for retrieval.",
    "Yu et al. (2023) also employed LM to determine the timing of retrieval."
  ]
}